Output assets/concurrent.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1920
Set Height 1080
Set Padding 30
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Theme "Dracula"

Type "# 20 API requests. One command. Let's go."
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "hulak -dir assets/demo/"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "# You can also run with -q flag to quiet the output"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "hulak -dir assets/demo/ -q"
Enter
Sleep 3s
